{"product_id":"madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-3-8g","title":"MÁDARA Dazzle Nights Satin Shine Lipstick, #501 Flattery 3,8g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrench your lips in dreamy, pigment-loaded colour and subtle lustre that pay homage to the glistening textures and bold hues of the 80s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe opulent, vegan formula made with nourishing oils, shea butter and vitamins C+E  goes on smooth, wearing off gradually and delicately while hydrating lips from the inside out. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic or animal-derived colourants. Dermatologically tested.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply directly to clean, moisturised lips. For an extra glossy finish, layer MÁDARA Glossy Venom Hydrating Lip Gloss on top.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e OCTYLDODECANOL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SORBITAN OLIVATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; DILINOLEIC ACID\/PROPANEDIOL COPOLYMER; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; MICA (CI 77019)***; AROMA; DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE; TOCOPHEROL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; LIMONENE**; TIN OXIDE (CI 77681)***; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ***; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e8% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52635897266503,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-38g-7415719.jpg?v=1762389193","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-3-8g","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}